<h2 class="wp-block-heading is-deco">On vous informe</h2>



<div class="wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile is-image-fill"><div class="wp-block-media-text__content"><?xml encoding="UTF-8"><p class="has-primary-color has-text-color has-link-color has-normal-font-size wp-elements-390500b2aaf7c01a03f7f21b42c8f13d wp-block-paragraph">Le CNAOP appelle l&rsquo;attention des personnes&hellip;</p>


<?xml encoding="UTF-8"><p class=" wp-block-paragraph">Le CNAOP appelle l&rsquo;attention des personnes en qu&ecirc;te de leurs origines sur les messages diffus&eacute;s sur les r&eacute;seaux sociaux. Il convient d&rsquo;&ecirc;tre particuli&egrave;rement vigilant sur les informations divulgu&eacute;es qui peuvent &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;es par des personnes mal intentionn&eacute;es &agrave; des fins malveillantes.</p>
</div><figure data-bg="https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-1024x683.jpg" class="wp-block-media-text__media rocket-lazyload" style="background-position:50% 50%"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="683" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20683'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-637 size-full" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-2048x1366.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-1024x683.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="683" src="https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-1024x683.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-637 size-full" srcset="https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.france-enfance-protegee.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/van-tay-media-TFFn3BYLc5s-unsplash-2048x1366.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></figure></div>
